name: Feature Implementation Workflow
description: Defines how to implement new features using the structured plan in implementation-plan.mdc.
globs: ["**/*.ts", "**/*.tsx", "implementation-plan.mdc"]

---

- For any new feature, follow the step-by-step instructions in `implementation-plan.mdc`.
- Complete steps in order, one at a time.
- After finishing a step, mark it as “Done” in `implementation-plan.mdc`.
- Add a two-line summary below the step describing what was done.
